frame Leave a battle

actor Student
activate Student

Student->System: 1: requestBattlePage()

activate System
System-->Student: 2: show(battle-page)
deactivate System

Student->System: 3: leaveBattle(battle)
alt signedIn == false
System-->Student: 4: show(not-signed-in Message)
else hasJoinedBattle == false
System-->Student: show(not-joined-battle Message)
else 
System->System: 5: removeStudent(student)
Student<--System: 6: ack
end
activate System

deactivate System
deactivate Student

